              "text": [ "Please choose the category (reply with the number or name):\n1. Incident Handling - Hardware\n2. Incident Handling - Identity Access\n3. Incident Handling - Information Security\n4. Incident Handling - Network\n5. Incident Handling - Software\n6. Service Request - Hardware\n7. Service Request - Identity Access\n8. Service Request - Information Security\n9. Service Request - Network\n10. Service Request - Software" ]
            },
            "languageCode": "en"
          }, {
            "text": {
              "text": [ "Silakan pilih kategori (balas dengan nomor atau nama):\n1. Penanganan Insiden - Perangkat Keras\n2. Penanganan Insiden - Akses Identitas\n3. Penanganan Insiden - Keamanan Informasi\n4. Penanganan Insiden - Jaringan\n5. Penanganan Insiden - Perangkat Lunak\n6. Permintaan Layanan - Perangkat Keras\n7. Permintaan Layanan - Akses Identitas\n8. Permintaan Layanan - Keamanan Informasi\n9. Permintaan Layanan - Jaringan\n10. Permintaan Layanan - Perangkat Lunak" ]
            },
            "languageCode": "id"
